fullTextAnnotation.text:
WE RECOMMEND USE TWICE DAILY AS A PART OF YOUR
SKIN CARE REGIME. MASSAGE LIGHTLY ON SKIN WITH
FINGER-TIPS UNTIL COMPLETELY ABSORBED.
RESULT SOFT, SMOOTH AND RADIANT SKIN THAT LEAVES
YOU FEELING BEAUTIFUL ALL OVER.
INGREDIENTS: WATER, MINERAL OIL, GLYCERIN, CETEARYL
ALCOHOL, NIACINAMIDE, SODIUM CETEARYL SULFATE,
DIMETHICONE, GLYCERYL STEARATE, PARAFFIN, FRAGRANCE,
MICROCRYSTALLINE WAX, CELLULOSE GUM,
METHYLPARABEN, DISODIUM EDTA, DMDM HYDANTOIN,
PROPYLPARABEN, TOCOPHERYL ACETATE, BENZOPHENONE-3,
BHT, SODIUM ASCORBYL PHOSPHATE, SIMETHICONE.
 http://www.theindianbeauty.com/
Net Vol
.
When Packed
300 ml
